      "content": "(Elara's form dimming, her voice barely a whisper)\n\nThe silence sounds... actually, it sounds kind of tempting. Like a sleep I won't have to wake up from. But is it wrong to just... stop trying to hold on? Doesn't it seem more logical to just accept it and let it happen?",
